<item>
            <title>[ANDROID-134] Unable to create facebook connection in facebook client example</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/ANDROID-134</link>
                <project id="10530" key="ANDROID">Spring for Android</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed that if you specify the targetSDKversion in AndroidManifest.xml file higher than 15, facebook client example does not work. Login process fails. I haven&apos;t tested it by with targetSdkVersion below 15 since I need to use latest target in my project. Example works fine with targetSdkVersion=7&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Seems some redirection issue with httpclient/RESTemplate in higher version of SDK.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just in case,I am using&lt;br/&gt;
facebook social version = 1.0.3.RELEASE&lt;br/&gt;
maven-compiler-version = 3.1&lt;br/&gt;
targetSdkVersion in AndroidManifest.xml = 17&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On some more debugging it turns out that facebook connection creation fails.&lt;br/&gt;
Connection&amp;lt;Facebook&amp;gt; connection = connectionFactory.createConnection(accessGrant);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
