                            <comment id="91548" author="rclarkson" created="Sun, 7 Jul 2013 20:06:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Spring Social makes a network request to Facebook when it creates the connection. In the sample app, this method call was happening on the main UI thread. Newer versions of Android disallow network requests on the UI thread, so this call has been moved into an AsyncTask.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
